{{#if hasPrisma}}
- Create new migration: `npx prisma migrate dev --name <descriptive_name>`
- Apply migrations (prod): `npx prisma migrate deploy`
- Generate Prisma Client: `npx prisma generate`
{{else if hasTypeORM}}
- Generate migration: `npx typeorm migration:generate -n <DescriptiveName>`
- Run migrations: `npx typeorm migration:run`
- Revert migration: `npx typeorm migration:revert`
{{else if hasDrizzle}}
- Generate migration: `npx drizzle-kit generate`
- Push schema to DB (dev): `npx drizzle-kit push`
- Run migrations (prod): `npx drizzle-kit migrate`
{{else if hasMikroORM}}
- Create migration: `npx mikro-orm migration:create`
- Run migrations: `npx mikro-orm migration:up`
{{else if hasKnex}}
- Make migration: `npx knex migrate:make <descriptive_name>`
- Run migrations: `npx knex migrate:latest`
- Rollback: `npx knex migrate:rollback`
{{/if}}
